@startuml
title State diagram of Video Suggestion System operations

[*] --> ReceivingRequest

state "Receiving a video suggestion request" as ReceivingRequest
state "Identifying User" as IdentifyingUser
state "Gathering videos" as GatheringVideos
state "Adding details" as AddingDetails
state "Sending suggested videos" as SendingSuggestedVideos

ReceivingRequest --> IdentifyingUser : receive request
IdentifyingUser --> GatheringVideos : identify user
GatheringVideos --> GatheringVideos : gather videos (user profile, trending, similar tags, genre, promoted)
GatheringVideos --> AddingDetails : gatherings complete
AddingDetails --> AddingDetails : add thumbnails and view counts
AddingDetails --> SendingSuggestedVideos : details added
SendingSuggestedVideos --> [*] : send suggested videos to user
@enduml
